  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels under the Minimal profile declaration. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. Decision: Accepted under Minimal profile. Package carries a content hash but no digital signature, reflecting ProfileMinimal conformance.",
