      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9) has a documented regression test suite and version-controlled release. SQA documentation meets the required level 3 threshold for MRL 5 Class III device assessment."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
