      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests on canonical flows must confirm solver convergence consistent with stated discretization scheme.",
      "rationale": "Second-order convergence confirmed via method-of-manufactured-solutions on pipe flow and rotating cavity benchmarks. Achieved level 3 satisfies the MRL 5 requirement."
    },
    {
